      <description>Winston Riddick was a political science professor at Louisiana State
            University and political ally of Gillis Long. Gillis Long (1923-1985) was representative
            for the 8th U.S. Congressional District of Louisiana in 1963-1965 and 1973-1985. He ran
            unsuccessfully for governor of Louisiana in 1964 and 1971.</description>
